                <p class="overview cursor-text">Le Petit Prince (The Little Prince) is philosophical tale, with humanist
                    values, shared from one generation to another for more than 75 years.　Written by Antoine de
                    Saint-Exupéry, this is the story of a grown-up meeting his inner child, embodied by a Little Prince.
                    I created this project as a small digital gallery for my favorite book. </p>
            </div>
            <div id="prince-goals" class="project-goals">
                <h3 class="goals-name cursor-text">goals —</h3>
                <p class="goals cursor-text">For this project, I wanted to design and code a 5-page website gallery for
                    The Little Prince. Through this project, I hope to create a fully-functioning website using
                    front-end programming languages (HTML, CSS, Javascript) to bring to the audience a well-designed
                    digital gallery of The Little Prince.</p>
            </div>
